8e27dd4b-3e5e-46fd-b4e0-179f9073f211	email_brain	# Tony's Email Priority Rules\n\n### Always Important\n- Emails about **pricing/cost** (video sales letters, service costs)\n- Emails flagged as **testing/system requests** (brain builds, triggers)\n- **Off-market real estate deals** (Chino property mentions)\n- **Contract updates** (amended contracts, legal documents)\n\n### Never Important\n- Generic or routine notifications without deal/cost context\n- Duplicate or low-signal versions of contract/property emails\n\n### Key Senders\n- **Fernando Perez** — Off-market deal sourcing (highest priority)\n- **Ethan Jolly** — Legal/contract matters\n- **Sebastian Calder** — Cost/pricing inquiries\n\n### Tony's Decision Principles\n- **Deal-focused**: Real estate opportunities and off-market properties rank high\n- **Financial clarity**: Pricing, costs, and contract terms matter\n- **Action-oriented**: Emails requesting decisions or containing deal specifics take priority\n- **Context matters**: Same subject line can flip importance based on context (see Chino/Contract patterns) — volume and framing suggest urgency signals in metadata or body may be key	2026-04-04 07:06:23.905
